SUMMARY:Cupcake & Wine Pairing at grandview
DESCRIPTION:We are excited to bring back Cupcake & Wine Pairings! Pairings will take place select Thursday & Friday evenings in April. Enjoy 4 of our delicious wines specially paired with 4 freshly baked mini cupcakes from local partner Rise Bake Shoppe! \n(Gluten Free available but please note that the pairing is NOT nut free) \nRESERVATIONS REQUIRED in advance. Tickets are available for the following dates/times:Thursdays in April: 4/9\, 4/16\, 4/23 at 5:30pm & 7pmFridays 4/10\, 4/17 at 5:30pm \nPlease purchase all tickets for your group on ONE order so that we can prepare proper seating arrangements
URL:https://grandviewwines.com/vineyard-event/cupcake-wine-pairing-at-grandview/2026-04-09/
LOCATION:Grandview Vineyard\, 1489 Grandview Rd\, Mount Joy\, PA\, 17552\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://grandviewwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Cupcake-pairing.jpg
END:VEVENT
