SUMMARY:Thursday Nights at grandview
DESCRIPTION:Join us Thursday evenings\, where you can come hang out with friends and enjoy wine\, beer & seasonal cocktails!  We also offer Thursday activities such as 1st Thursday Trivia\, 2nd Thursday Yoga\, Charcuterie classes\, Glass blowing classes\, Macramé\, Plant night\, Paint night & MORE!  Some require advanced registration/tickets.   Additional info will be posted as events are scheduled.
