SUMMARY:Spring Deck Opening Celebration at grandview
DESCRIPTION:Let’s kick off our Wine by the Vine ON DECK season with a little fun! Join us for our deck opening Friday April 24th with music by The Nobles 6-8:30 pm AND Saturday April 25th with music by Corina Rose 2-5pm and Blake Hillard Duo 6-8:30pm. \nWe’ll have specialty cocktails\, drink specials and deck passes ON SALE Buy one get one 1/2 off Friday 5-9pm and Saturday 12-9pm! (on-site only) Free Admission. 1st come 1st serve seating.\nGourmet Julia’s Way Food truck on site Saturday 1:30-7pm
URL:https://grandviewwines.com/vineyard-event/spring-deck-opening-weekend-celebration-at-grandview/2026-04-24/
LOCATION:Grandview Vineyard\, 1489 Grandview Rd\, Mount Joy\, PA\, 17552\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://grandviewwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Wine-By-the-Vine-Deck-Series-5.jpg
END:VEVENT
