SUMMARY:Music Bingo at grandview
DESCRIPTION:Our Music Bingo is a ton of fun\, and best of all\, no music knowledge is needed! We mix in all decades and all genres so there’s something for everyone. Each player gets their own bingo card and each table gets a master sheet so you can keep track of what’s been played. We’ll play a 30 second clip of a song\, announce the title\, and if it’s on your card\, you cross it off. Expect a lot of singing and dancing along\, which just adds to the fun! Come out for a great time and your shot at winning some awesome prizes! \nHere’s how it works!! Due to limited seating inside during the winter months\, it is recommended that you reserve a table in advance. In order to guarantee a seat\, reserve your seat with only $5/table for a team up to 4. If you have more than 4 people\, you will need to purchase a second ticket so we can reserve a table with enough seating. \n Important: Please put your team size in your order notes so that we can best prepare the tables for each group! \nClick Here to Reserve a Table
URL:https://grandviewwines.com/vineyard-event/music-bingo-at-grandview-2/
LOCATION:Grandview Vineyard\, 1489 Grandview Rd\, Mount Joy\, PA\, 17552\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://grandviewwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Grandview_Mingo_Apr30.jpg
END:VEVENT
